<view class="page"><view class="hero"><view class="hero__badge">MPX × DIMINA</view><view class="hero__title">Mpx 兼容性示例</view><view class="hero__description">使用 Mpx 官方 createPage / createComponent 写法构建，并交由 Dimina 运行。</view></view><view class="panel"><view class="panel__label">页面计算属性</view><view class="panel__value">{{fullName}}</view><view class="counter">当前 {{count}}，双倍 {{doubleCount}}</view><button bindtap="increment" class="primary-button">计数 +1</button></view><view class="panel"><view class="panel__label">延迟条件渲染</view><button bindtap="toggleDeferred" class="secondary-button">{{showDeferred ? '隐藏' : '显示'}}延迟计算属性</button><view class="deferred-result" wx:if="{{showDeferred}}">{{deferredLabel}}</view></view><summary-card count="{{count}}" prefix="子组件计数"/></view>